channel.title: Help with ::char
channel.description: i just got testscape (was originally using p 16) and i went to go do ::cahr and it wont let me click teh accept button :mad: so what do i put?

item.title: Help with ::char
item.dc:creator: @Billys_Java Billys Java
item.description:
@Billys_Java wrote:

you have to get the char button to work so go into your client.java and search for this

//case 4126: windstrike break;

and right below it add this case

case 14067: // Char design accept button RemoveAllWindows(); break;

then save compile and run it should work now
